separator.info:
The character to split on. Use 
 for newline. Examples: 

 for paragraphs, 
 for lines, . for sentences

filter_expression.info:
Optional JSON to control filters/limit/score threshold.
Accepted shapes:
1) {"filter": [ {"term": {"filename":"foo"}}, {"terms":{"owner":["u1","u2"]}} ], "limit": 10, "score_threshold": 1.6 }
2) Context-style maps: {"data_sources":["fileA"], "document_types":["application/pdf"], "owners":["123"]}
Placeholders with __IMPOSSIBLE_VALUE__ are ignored.
